Format 60
Input stdclass.inc

SecNumDepth             2
TocDepth                2

NoStyle Chapter
NoCounter chapter
NoStyle Chapter*


Style Part
	Align                 Left
	AlignPossible         Left
	TopSep                2
	BottomSep             1.5
	Font
	  Size                Larger
	EndFont
End


Style Part*
	Align                 Left
	AlignPossible         Left
	TopSep                2
	BottomSep             1.5
	Font
	  Size                Larger
	EndFont
End
